com.freshbourne.multimap.btree
Class DynamicDataPage

java.lang.Object
  com.freshbourne.multimap.btree.DynamicDataPage
All Implemented Interfaces:
Page, DataPage
public class DynamicDataPage
extends java.lang.Object
implements DataPage

Wraps around a byte[] and can hold values. Since its a dynamic data page, values are written first at the end of the body to allow the header to grow. The PagePointer of the header are kept in Memory
